data.title: About: WBON
data.meta_description: WBON-LD is a digital low power television station serving portions of east-central Kentucky, including the Lexington area. Licensed to Richmond with a transmitter near Waco, the station is owned by Wallingford Broadcasting, Inc. The station's digital signal is broadcast on digital VHF channel 9. It shares a broadcast tower with co-owned FM stations WCYO and WLFX.
